          <title>Egor Demin sets NBA rookie 3-point record as Nets snap 7-game skid with 109-99 win over Jazz</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Egor Demin set an NBA rookie record by making a 3-pointer in his 34th straight game and finished with 25 points and 10 rebounds to help the Brooklyn Nets snap a seven-game losing streak with a 109-99 victory over the Utah Jazz.]]></description>
